OL,3,CWales' biggest health board to stay in
OL,4,Cspecial measures despite 'some'
OL,5,Cprogress
OL,7,FIt means that the troubled North Wales
OL,8,Fhealth board has been receiving the
OL,9,Fhighest level of support and
OL,10,Finterventions since 27 February 2023.
OL,12,FDespite progress in a range of areas,
OL,13,Fincluding culture, leadership and
OL,14,Fgovernance, and quality and safety,
OL,15,Fthere "are still challenges" in the
OL,16,Fhealth board, particularly around
OL,17,Fplanned care performance and timely
OL,18,Faccess to urgent and emergency care,
OL,19,Faccording to a new report published on
OL,20,FTuesday (4 March).
