OL,7,FHe said: "I want to commend the
OL,8,Fstaff's commitment and determination
OL,9,Fto make meaningful improvements to
OL,10,Fhealth services for the people
OL,11,Fthroughout North Wales.
OL,13,FHe continued: "I have seen first-hand
OL,14,Fexamples of the excellent work taking
OL,15,Fplace, but we know there is more to do
OL,16,Fto improve the experience of staff,
OL,17,Fpatients and their families."
